
Prerequesites:-
===============
install npm, nodejs, serve
install nginx
edit sites-available

server {
listen 80 default_server;
root /var/www/my.app;
server_name IP ;
index index.html index.htm;
location / {
}
}

1) Create a directory my.app
2) got my.app and run npm init
3) add serve PATH, absolute path of serve
run serv -s build &

restart nginx n try login http://IP


